P02 Ad Copy Generation 

# Prompt 2 – Digital Marketing

## Version 2 (v2.1)

### Prompt
Write a Google ad for kitchen equipment.

Respond 

**Headline 1:** Upgrade Your Café Equipment Today
**Headline 2:** No Upfront Costs with Flexikitch
**Headline 3:** Flexible Rent-to-Own Solutions

**Description:**
Get high-quality kitchen equipment without the large upfront expense. Flexikitch offers flexible payment plans, easy upgrades, and maintenance support. Perfect for growing cafés.

**CTA:**
Book Your Free Consultation Today

**Path:**
flexikitch.com.au/cafe-equipment

**Keywords:**
café equipment, kitchen equipment rental, rent to own kitchen, hospitality equipment, commercial kitchen solutions


### Change Made
Basic instruction with no targeting or structure and generic ad copy with no clear audience or value

### Observed Effect
Low relevance, weak engagement, not usable for real campaigns

### Lesson Learned
Ads require targeting, benefits and CTA


## Version 2 (v2.2)

### Prompt
As a paid ads specialist. Write a Google ad for Flexikitch targeting owners in hospitality industry. Include headline, description, benefits CTA but no upfront cost and flexibility. Keep persuasive and concise.

Respoond
**Headline 1:** Hospitality Equipment Without Upfront Cost
**Headline 2:** Flexible Kitchen Solutions for Your Business
**Headline 3:** Upgrade Your Café or Restaurant Today

**Description:**
Get the equipment you need now—without upfront costs. Flexikitch offers flexible payment options, easy upgrades, and ongoing support to keep your kitchen running smoothly. Perfect for growing hospitality businesses.

**Benefits:**
✔ No upfront cost
✔ Flexible payment plans
✔ Upgrade as you grow

**CTA:**
Book Your Free Consultation Today


### Change Made
Added role (ads specialist) , added structure (headline, description, CTA), and added constraints (concise, persuasive)

### Observed Effect
High-quality, usable ad copy and consistent structure across outputs

### Lesson Learned
Structured prompts improve conversion focused outputs
